data.title: Weather in Tyumen in October
data.meta_description: Average weather for Tyumen in October. Including Average Temperatures,Average number of rainy days and a general information about the weather in Tyumen in October
data.text:
The weather in Tyumen in October is cold, when degrees are between -1 and 7 and there are 9 days of rain and 8 days of snow in average. Therefore, if you are planning a trip to Tyumen in October, warm clothes and gloves are highly recommended.

Weather Facts - Tyumen in October

* The warmest temperature recorded in in October is 23°C

* The coldest temperature recorded in Tyumen in October is (-14°C)

* The average rainfall in Tyumen in October is 24 mm
